title: G4H is different from the example
body:
```

cat test.fa
>testfa
TTGGGTTGGGACTGGGTACGGGAATAAATAGGTTAGGAATGGATAGGAT

python G4Catchall.py -f test.fa --G3L 1..3 --G4H

testfa  2       22      20      +       GGGTTGGGACTGGGTACGGG    GGGTTGGGACTGGGTACGGG    0.45
```
While the G4H in the example is 2.11.
